    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * David Blackman</b>\n</p><p><b>David Blackman</b>,<br />\nan Australian chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, software developer, and as computer chess programmer author of the chess program <a href=\"/Desperado\" title=\"Desperado\">Desperado</a>, which has been under development since 1989, and played in most of the <a href=\"/Australasian_National_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"Australasian National Computer Chess Championship\">NC3 tournaments</a>, and all the <a href=\"/ANU_Carbon-Silicon_Tournaments\" title=\"ANU Carbon-Silicon Tournaments\">ANU Carbon-Silicon Tournaments</a> before..\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1995...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_....\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ....</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Blackman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995...\">1995...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Blackman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1995...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/fedfcfaf26d04dfa\">Re: Quiescence search problems</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 3, 1995&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/Integrated_Bounds_and_Values\" title=\"Integrated Bounds and Values\">Integrated Bounds and Values</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/ba9febc300f8698f\">Re: How to get chess program to solve KBN mate?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David John Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, September 18, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/KnightCap\" title=\"KnightCap\">KnightCap</a>, <a href=\"/KBNK_Endgame\" title=\"KBNK Endgame\">KBNK Endgame</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=16697\">Re: National computer chess championship, Australia, July 1998</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 08, 1998</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_....\">2000 ....</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Blackman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ....\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=87251\">Re: Australian-ch, questions&#160;!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 09, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/NC3_1999\" title=\"NC3 1999\">NC3 1999</a>, <a href=\"/Australasian_National_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"Australasian National Computer Chess Championship\">Australasian National Computer Chess Championship</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=105974\">Re: What Chess programs existed in the '60s?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 13, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Mac_Hack\" title=\"Mac Hack\">Mac Hack VI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=105999\">Re: What Chess programs existed in the '60s?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 14, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Kaissa\" title=\"Kaissa\">Kaissa</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=109165\">NC3 tournament, Australia</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 05, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/NC3_2000\" title=\"NC3 2000\">NC3 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=179834\">Nc3 Australia</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">David Blackman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/NC3_2001\" title=\"NC3 2001\">NC3 2001</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesschat.org//showpost.php?p=63437&amp;postcount=10\">Re: 2005 National Computer Chess Championships</a> by <a href=\"/Shaun_Press\" title=\"Shaun Press\">Shaun Press</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesschat.org/archive/index.php/\">Chess Chat</a>, July 17, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Point_Value\" title=\"Point Value\">Point Value</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Blackman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.365chess.com/players/David_Blackman\">David Blackman chess games - 365Chess.com</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Blackman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.365chess.com/players/David_Blackman\">David Blackman chess games - 365Chess.com</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301153311\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 37/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 74/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in